==English==
===Etymology===
From "[[God|(God')s]] [[truth]]". Compare [[zounds]], [[blimey]].

===Interjection===
'''strewth!'''

# (''Australia'', ''UK''<!-- Other parts? -->) A mild oath expressing surprise or generally adding emphasis.
#: '''''Strewth'''! I guess I've been too trigger happy!''
